Subject: [PATCH 76/95] NVIDIA: SAUCE: soc/tegra: fuse: Add FUSE_USB_CALIB_EXT2
 and FUSE_USB_CALIB_EXT3

Add FUSE_USB_CALIB_EXT2 and FUSE_USB_CALIB_EXT3 which are used for USB
calibration.

http://nvbugs/4933929

Upstream-Status: Backport
Signed-off-by: Wayne Chang <waynec@nvidia.com>
Reviewed-by: Henry Lin <henryl@nvidia.com>
Reviewed-by: Sing-Han Chen <singhanc@nvidia.com>
Reviewed-by: WK Tsai <wtsai@nvidia.com>
Reviewed-by: HaoTien Hsu <haotienh@nvidia.com>
Signed-off-by: Vishwaroop A <va@nvidia.com>
Acked-by: Noah Wager <noah.wager@canonical.com>
Acked-by: Jacob Martin <jacob.martin@canonical.com>
Signed-off-by: Noah Wager <noah.wager@canonical.com>
(cherry picked from commit d3157ee1dc0c336701c5f9cf7c9a499041890b50)
Signed-off-by: Matt Madison <matt@madison.systems>
---
 include/soc/tegra/fuse.h | 2 ++
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+)

diff --git a/include/soc/tegra/fuse.h b/include/soc/tegra/fuse.h
index 8f421b9f7585..5a112763457a 100644
--- a/include/soc/tegra/fuse.h
+++ b/include/soc/tegra/fuse.h
@@ -23,6 +23,8 @@
 #define TEGRA_FUSE_SKU_CALIB_0	0xf0
 #define TEGRA30_FUSE_SATA_CALIB	0x124
 #define TEGRA_FUSE_USB_CALIB_EXT_0 0x250
+#define TEGRA_FUSE_USB_CALIB_EXT2_0 0x2ec
+#define TEGRA_FUSE_USB_CALIB_EXT3_0 0x3bc
 
 #ifndef __ASSEMBLY__
 
